%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant Gateway as Data Science Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager
    participant Head as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS
    participant Worker as Ray Worker Pod
    participant Serve as Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: RayJob Submission (HTTPMode)
    User->>Gateway: POST /v1/jobs<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (8443/TCP)<br/>TLS
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Forward (8265/TCP)<br/>HTTP plaintext (localhost)
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: Job accepted
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Job ID

    Operator->>Dashboard: Poll job status<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP
    Dashboard-->>Operator: Job status
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob status<br/>HTTPS, SA Token

    Note over Operator,Worker: Flow 2: RayCluster Provisioning
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Services, RBAC<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create Issuer + Certificates<br/>(if mTLS enabled)
    CertMgr-->>Operator: Certs provisioned
    Worker->>Head: Connect to GCS (6379/TCP)<br/>gRPC, mTLS (if enabled)
    Worker->>Head: Dashboard agent (52365/TCP)<br/>HTTP

    Note over User,Serve: Flow 3: RayService Serve Traffic
    User->>Serve: Inference request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    Serve->>Head: Route to serve replica<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    Head-->>Serve: Response
    Serve-->>User: Prediction result
